ygData.messageBody:
Actually you will be quite surprised to know that there are a lot of
creatures still blue in Sol A at 37th. The throne room(where solusek
goblins, solusek mages, and solusek champions spawn) is almost totally blue
still. As well, if you hate gnomes, the gnome castle is full of blue
clockworks and gnomes(this is where charred armor comes from). Anyway, just
wanted to let you know that Sol A is still good into the upper 30's but by
this time you may want to think about moving to B unless you are still in
need of items.

Yours,

~Aereuss Ravins of Tarew Marr
